30/Jul/25 7:50 PM;gvamsik;Hi [~vleung1]  

 
Here are the sample AVRO messages. The schemas have been uploaded to Nexus; please use version 2.12.
 
{code:java}
<dependency>    
<groupId>com.sonymusic.global.ds</groupId>   
<artifactId>AvroSchemas</artifactId>    
<version>2.12-SNAPSHOT</version> 
</dependency>
{code}
 
Sample Message :
{code:java}
{
  "header" : {
    "namespace" : "DDEX",
    "sendingSystem" : "ASSET_INGESTER",
    "messageContext" : "METADATA_IMPORT",
    "messageType" : "METADATA_IMPORT_EVENT",
    "messageId" : "d52b1824-f89c-4342-bd0c-c5eaaf2422fb",
    "globalCorrelationId" : "c014b2dd-511c-42da-bf24-0b2687eca046",
    "correlationId" : "51ca72cd-67e9-48ca-a861-6c599dce8016",
    "messageKey" : {
      "string" : "TqYShKl8J"
    },
    "createDateTime" : 1753896700286,
    "eventTimestamp" : 1753896700286,
    "tags" : null
  },
  "payload" : {
    "catalogKey" : "8jIF2Z",
    "documentType" : "PRODUCT_METADATA",
    "status" : "FAILED",
    "upc" : {
      "string" : "5JhoB7x"
    },
    "configKey" : {
      "string" : "jzWpoC6Dx"
    },
    "isComplete" : {
      "boolean" : false
    },
    "error" : {
      "com.sonymusic.global.ds.schema.avro.common.Error" : {
        "code" : "ERROR_CODE",
        "severity" : "WARNING",
        "message" : "ERROR_MESSAGE"
      }
    }
  }
}

{code}
In the AVRO schema, we've added UPC, IsCompleteFl, and ConfigKey ( NULL is valid value ) . This information will be beneficial for Mobile Auto linking and DDEX - Asset flow. Including these fields in the message will help avoid unnecessary callbacks.
 

Schema also has failure object , I think we would to good to publish failed events as well and DDEX can record failures for DDEX UPCs . 
 
Let me know if you have any questions or concerns . ;;;
